{"type": "article", "id": 14352, "title": "全是银色的！Thom Browne把这家快闪店叫“克制的挥霍”", "description": "就是那个通吃小鲜肉和成熟大叔的 Thom Browne", "date": "2015-09-03T08:02:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 3703, "name": "现代"}, {"id": 35, "name": "复古"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 121, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702141723MSf86mhjvkw9oOs1.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t时尚品牌 <a href=\"http://www.lebonmarche.com/marques/thom-browne.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thom Browne 最近在著名的巴黎百货商店 Le Bon Marché Rive Gauche 有一间快闪店</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141717HEvrOSI6niYUcM8p.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021417180e5y1akF34XsRTdU.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141718IBN17KOkw9hLQiG6.jpg\" width=\"955\" height=\"568\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5947644\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t内部以 50 年代的办公室为灵感， 但又未来感十足。Thom Browne 无数双带着标志性红白蓝条纹的银色牛津鞋中间，是一个全金属的办公桌，包括桌子上的打印机、台灯等等一切都是银色——而这个装置曾经在本季秋冬秀场的广告大片中出现过。Le Bon Marché 百货店称这种风格为 “克制的挥霍（controlled extravagance）”。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141718TukeQjtipZ3VoNaR.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141719OmyMo6sr103Z9txH.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t2001 年由 Thom Browne 创立的同名品牌，一出现就以强烈的个人风格为男士正装带来了突破——比如必须长度在脚踝以上的西裤（并且紧贴着腿），看起来像小了一号的西装外套，而且前襟总是三粒纽扣。这些优雅、经典的款式上小小的革新，令热爱时尚的人群纷纷沦陷。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021417190Kj2suHrA9tvy7cE.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"350\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>包括娱乐圈的小鲜肉、韩流明星、前辈们都频频撞衫</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141720JMDrQu3nyep7mjF2.jpg\" width=\"514\" height=\"420\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81712062\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141720YhuFImnp4b3zEgOL.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141721XodI9um0BTJQLbWD.jpg\" width=\"621\" height=\"350\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56360709\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141721gDXm5Y8O2sjELySR.jpg\" width=\"1034\" height=\"698\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67504836\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141722pvxHB0qGrdnyUIfV.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\">Thom Browne 将选出最经典的单品在这里展卖，从 8 月 29 至 9 月期间。部分款式可以<a href=\"http://www.lebonmarche.com/marques/thom-browne.html\" target=\"_blank\">在官网上购买</a>。</span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141722QN6nS3gOhDqVPjL2.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:justify;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021417235L9W1BmG2tiQvxPY.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:left;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n"}